
== Visual effect and wagon power (10) ==
{{en/CB|features=trains, road vehicles, ships|purchase=no|result=selected effect|fail=default properties}}


To wywołanie zwrotne służy do określenia efektu wizualnego, jaki ma być zastosowany w pojeździe oraz do tego, czy wagon jest napędzany (dodając moc i wagę do pociągu).

The 'powered wagon'-flag only applies for train wagons that would by default be powered (i.e. property 1B is set).

The visual effect applies to all train vehicles ({{pl/Development/NewGRF/ottd|1.1|r21238}} Since OpenTTD r21238 for road vehicles and ships as well).

Oddzwanianie jest wywoływane tylko podczas ładowania gry, kiedy pociąg się cofa lub podczas przestawiania pociągu w depocie.

{{pl/Development/NewGRF/ottd| }} In OpenTTD the 'visual effect' is also updated when the vehicle enters track of a different railtype. The 'powered wagon'-flag may not change in that case.

If the callback fails for any reason (e.g. not defined, action 2 does not return callback result etc.), the value of the corresponding action 0 property ( [[pl/Development/NewGRF/NFO Specs/Action0/Vehicles/Trains#visual-effects-and-wagon-power-22|train property 22]], [[pl/Development/NewGRF/NFO Specs/Action0/Vehicles/RoadVehicles#visual-effect-21|road vehicle property 21]], [[pl/Development/NewGRF/NFO Specs/Action0/Vehicles/Ships#visual-effect-1c|ship property 1C]] ) is used instead. &nbsp;For possible return values, refer to these properties as well.
